hikatta yume o ageru yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:46.90,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Le daré a tu corazón\Nque late{\i0}\N{\i1}un sueño brillante\Ny resplandeciente!{\i0}
